{"tid":523150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[發達大計- 六合彩]   有5000萬賭本既巴打，可以拎$10 出黎買六合彩","createTime":"2018-01-08T09:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T01:58:31.000Z","uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4f12d080fe8ace7ab6c26b01253d6c9e47c81c","tid":523150,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"根據15年  (2003-2017) 以來既數據 , <br />\n攪出次數最少的號碼為<span style=\"color: red;\">19號</span>，只有276次；第二少為286次的<span style=\"color: red;\">23號</span>。<br />\n所以大家可以放心無視呢兩個number <br />\n<br />\n另外大家都知, 好多人買六合彩會買連續數 , e.g. 1,2,3,4,5,6 ; 2,3,4,5,6,7 <br />\n一來呢d 唔易中, 就算中都冇肉食 <br />\n所以我地可以無視呢d  pattern 既飛 <br />\n<br />\n\b<br />\n綜合以上既技術去調整風險後<br />\n六合彩中頭獎機會率 <br />\n= 1/{(1/[(6/47)*(5/46)*(4/45)*(3/44)*(2/43)*(1/42)*])-42}<br />\n=1/10737531 <br />\n<br />\n聽晚1月9號, <br />\n頭獎獎金有1億1千萬 <br />\n用kelly criterion 計 <br />\n= [(10999999*100/10737531)-(100-100/10737531)]/10999999<br />\n=0.0000222% <br />\n<br />\n\b若果巴打有5千萬賭本 , $5千萬 * 0.0000222%  = $11.1 <br />\n由於馬會淨係買到$10注  , 所以有 $ 5千萬買 $10 就岩架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/101320/%E5%85%AD%E5%90%88%E5%BD%A949%E5%80%8B%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E6%94%AA%E8%B6%B315%E5%B9%B4-%E6%94%AA%E5%87%BA%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E4%BF%82-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F101320%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%25BD%25A949%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E6%2594%25AA%25E8%25B6%25B315%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%2594%25AA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BF%2582-&d=AQXv8v5zrInziDiuWMdLC26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=